  <thing id="xHarmbPosi" name="Harmed by Positive Energy" description="A kir-lanan suffers damage from {i}cure wounds spells{/i}, {i}holy water{/i}, and {i}blessed weapons{/i} just as if she were undead.  Conversely, she is healed by {i}inflict wounds{/i} spells and other applications of negative energy.  Kir-lanans are {b}{u}NOT UNDEAD{/u}{/b}, but their bodies are infused with negative energy.  They cannot be turned, but they are uncomfortable around such displays and usually seek to avoid a turning cleric any how." compset="Special" summary="Harmed by positive energy, healed by negative.  Cannot be turned.">
