  <thing id="gCrystCalt" name="Caltrops, Crystal" description="These special caltrops are made out of a tough crystal. These are deployed just like traditional caltrops.\nWhen they score a hit, they do normal damage and release a poisonous gas. The victim must make a Fortitude save (DC 12) or instantly fall asleep for 1 minute. After 1 minute, the target must make another Fortitude save (DC 12) or sleep for an additional 1d4 minutes. The gas affects creatures immune to magical sleep, but not creatures immune to poison." compset="Gear" summary="Releases a sleep gas when stepped on, DC 12.">
