  <thing id="ipCooling" name="Cooling" description="Cooling: This metal armor seems cool to the touch, no matter what the environment. The wearer of such armor gains fire resistance 5. At the cost of increasing the armor&#146;s cost by another +1 property, this ability can be upgraded to the fire resistance ability described in the {i}DUNGEON MASTER&#146;S Guide{/i}.\n\nCaster Level: 3rd; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}endure elements{/i}; Market Price: +1 bonus." compset="ItemPower" summary="+5 Fire resistance.">
