  <thing id="ipWarming" name="Warming" description="Warming: This metal armor seems warm to the touch, no matter what the environment. The wearer of such armor gains cold resistance 5. At the cost of increasing the armor&#146;s cost by another +1 property, this ability can be upgraded to the cold resistance ability described in the DUNGEON MASTER&#146;S Guide.\n\nCaster Level: 3rd; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}endure elements{/i}; Market Price: +1 bonus." compset="ItemPower">
