  <thing id="ipBerserk" name="Berserker (Races of Faerun)" description="Berserker: A berserker weapon is particularly valuable to barbarians and other creatures who can enter a rage. When the wielder is raging, the weapon&#146;s enhancement bonus increases by +2.\n\nCaster Level: 7th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}divine power{/i} or {i}emotion{/i}; Market Price: +1 bonus." compset="ItemPower" summary="Grants an additional +2 while in a rage." uniqueness="useronce">
