  <thing id="iEarthskin" name="Earthskin" description="Earthskin: This +1 dendritic armor is fashioned by urdunnir dwarves, who can simply stone walk into and out of the living crystal armor whenever they don&#146;t need to wear it.  Others just succeed on a Strength check (DC 22) to break out of the armor.\nIf even part of the earthskin survives damage, however, it regrows in 8 hours.\nCaster Level: 3rd; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor; Market Price: 3,150 gp; Cost to Create: 2,650 gp + 40 XP." compset="MagicArmor" summary="+1 Dendritic Armor">
