  <thing id="iAxeSeaRea" name="Axe of the Sea Reavers" description="This +2 greataxe of Illuskan manufacture gives its wielder the ability to float atop the water, no matter what his weight. Furthermore, the wielder can, with the war cry engraved into the haft, give all allies within 15 feet a +2 morale bonus on saving throws, attack rolls, ability checks, skill checks, and weapon damage rolls for one round. By saying the command word engraved on the blade itself, the wielder can force all foes within 15 feet to make a Will save (DC 16) or flee, as the {i}emotion (fear){/i} spell from a 7th-level \ncaster. The war cry and the command word can each be used once per day.\n\nMarket Price: 13,920 gp; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, emotion; Cost to Create: 7,120 gp + 544 XP." compset="MagicWep" summary="+2 grants float on water, +2 to allies; DC 16 Will or flee for foes.">
