  <thing id="iKerrendAr" name="Kerrenderit Arrows" description="Fashioned by the arctic dwarves, these +1 arrows are made from ice crystals from the Great Glacier. Kerrenderit arrows have the wounding special ability (see {i}DUNGEON MASTER&#146;s Guide{/i}). In addition, they have a range increment 25 feet farther than normal arrows. If kerrenderit arrows are exposed to temperatures above 50 degrees for more than 1 hour, their icy arrowheads melt into uselessness.\nCaster Level: 12th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}chill metal{/i}, creator must have access to arctic dwarf ice caves; Market Price: 350 gp; Cost to Create: 172 gp + 14 XP." compset="MagicWep">
