  <thing id="iScimSiroc" name="Scimitar of the Sirocco" description="Graced by a pommel shaped like the head of a desert hawk, this elegant and graceful weapon is a +1 keen scimitar.  It also doubles the speed of any horse or equine creature the bearer rides, much like {i}horseshoes of speed{/i}.\nCaster Level: 8th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}haste{/i}, {i}keen edge{/i}, creator must be Calishite; Market Price: 9,530 gp; Cost to Create: 4,922 gp + 367 XP." compset="MagicWep" summary="+1 keen scimitar, doubles the speed of any equine creature ridden.">
