  <thing id="iSpeaImpal" name="Spear of Impaling" description="Spear of Impaling: These +1 wounding shortspears are deadly to elves and dwarves. If the spear hits an elf or dwarf, the target must succeed at a Reflex save (DC 19) or be impaled by the spear (treat as an extra attack from the spear that hits automatically but cannot score a critical hit).\nCaster Level: 12th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}divine power{/i}; Market Price: 32,301 gp; Cost to Create: 16,301 gp + 640 XP." compset="MagicWep" summary="+1 Wounding Shortspear, deadly to to Elves and Dwarves.">
