  <thing id="iTridSeren" name="Trident of Serenity" description="Trident of Serenity: A +1 trident, this item has the additional quality of suppressing any effects or class features within 15 feet that rely on anger or fear, including a barbarian&#146;s ability to rage, a sahuagin blood frenzy, and a black dragon&#146;s frightful presence.\nCaster Level: 5th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, emotion; Market Price: 5,315 gp; Cost to Create: 2,815 gp + 200 XP." compset="MagicWep" summary="+1 Trident, Suppresses all effects that rely on anger or fear in 15ft.">
