  <thing id="ipOintBark" name="Ointment of Barkskin" description="Ointment of Barkskin: The wild dwarves of Chult use this greasy ointment. When slathered over the user&#146;s skin, it protects her with a barkskin spell.\nCaster Level: 5th; Prerequisites: Brew Potion, {i}barkskin{/i}; market Price: 300 gp; Weight: &#150;." compset="OilPotion" summary="Applies {i}barkskin{/i} as spell.">
