  <thing id="sClrStoBod" name="Stone Body" description="As {i}iron body{/i} except as below.\nYou gain damage reduction 20/+2. You are vulnerable to all special attacks that affect stone golems. You gain a +4 enhancement bonus to Strength and a &#150;4 penalty to Dexterity (to a \nminimum Dexterity score of 1).\nYour speed is reduced to half normal. Your weight increases by a factor of three.\n\n{b}Arcane Material Component:{/b} A small piece of stone that was once part of either a stone golem, a greater earth elemental, or a castle&#146;s outer wall." compset="Spell" summary="Your body becomes living stone." replaces="sClrStBody">
